aa(lp56
VThe best way to learn about anything
p57
aVis through stories, and so I want to tell you a story
p58
aVabout work and play and about four aspects of life
p59
aVthat we need to embrace
p60
aVin order for our own creativity to flourish.
p61
aVThe first embrace is something that we think,
p62
aV"Oh, this is very easy," but it's actually getting harder,
p63
aVand that's paying attention to the world around us.
p64
aVSo many artists speak about needing to be open,
p65
aVto embrace experience, and that's hard to do when
p66
aVyou have a lighted rectangle in your pocket that
p67
