VRichard Serra: I was standing there looking at it,
p151
aVand I realized that Velázquez was looking at me,
p152
aVand I thought, "Oh. I'm the subject of the painting."
p153
aVAnd I thought, "I'm not going to be able to do that painting."
p154
aVI was to the point where I was using a stopwatch
p155
aVand painting squares out of randomness,
p156
aVand I wasn't getting anywhere. So I went back and dumped
